nodes.text: The Nebula Front squadron was a starfighter unit of the militant wing serving Nebula Front that fielded Z-95 Headhunters, the predecessor to the X-wing. The fighter craft of the unit were painted white and marked with Nebula Front's blue logo on the wing panels. Made up of the veteran fighter pilots, the best aces were occasionally selected to be attached to the Nebula Elite, an exclusive squadron of the organization's top-ranking pilots.
